\cf2 Recommendation 3: Consider Adaptive Testing Elements (Long-Term): As a future enhancement, explore the integration of Computer Adaptive Testing (CAT) principles. Similar to assessments like the ACTFL L&RCAT [16, 17], a CAT system would adjust the difficulty of diagnostic questions based on the user's real-time performance. Correct answers lead to slightly harder questions, while incorrect answers lead to slightly easier ones, efficiently converging on an accurate proficiency estimate.\
