\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Rationale: CoT has been shown to improve the quality and coherence of LLM outputs for complex reasoning tasks.[46] It can lead to more thoughtful and relevant mnemonics. Additionally, exposing the "reasoning" (even if simulated) can offer transparency and potentially help users understand 
