\cf2 Recommendation 17: Contextual Tone Application: Ensure the prompt logic applies the selected tone consistently across all generated elements for a given flashcard. A highly serious phrase (slider=5) shouldn't typically have a wildly ridiculous mnemonic. Conversely, a comedic phrase (slider=95) benefits most from a humorous mnemonic and example sentence that match its playful nature. The system should strive for tonal coherence within each card.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0
