\f0\b\fs32 \cf2 C. Crafting Effective Mnemonics and Examples: Research-Based Strategies\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0 \cf2 Leveraging Cognitive Principles: Effective mnemonic devices function by forging strong, memorable associative links between new information (e.g., a Thai phrase) and existing knowledge or easily recalled cues.[4, 50, 57] Key cognitive principles underpinning successful mnemonics include leveraging vivid visualization, exploiting the memorability of the peculiar or unusual, and connecting new information to personal experiences or pre-existing knowledge structures.[4, 49, 50, 57]\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\cf2 Recommendation 19: Prompt for Vivid Visualization: Explicitly instruct the LLM to generate mnemonics that evoke strong, concrete visual imagery.[49, 50, 51, 52, 57] Encourage the use of specific nouns, active verbs, and sensory details. Prompts could request descriptions suitable for visualization, potentially even linking them conceptually to the app's AI-generated set images.[57]\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
