\f1\b0\fs32 \cf2 The Donkey Bridge app possesses a strong foundation with its focus on personalization, humor, and mnemonic techniques. However, achieving true didactic excellence requires moving beyond surface-level personalization towards a deeply integrated, research-informed system.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\cf2 This report outlines a strategic roadmap centered on:\
