\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Robust Assessment: Replacing static levels with dynamic proficiency assessment (Can-Do statements, diagnostics) linked to standardized frameworks (ACTFL/CEFR) and building a dynamic user skill profile.[5, 7, 13, 18]\
