\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Intelligent Content Generation: Employing sophisticated LLM prompting (structured architecture, role-playing, scaffolding, CoT) and potentially RAG to generate content truly tailored to the learner's profile, goals, and desired tone, ensuring pedagogical soundness and accuracy.[1, 2, 31, 35, 37, 38, 41, 46]\
\ls41\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	4	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
