\cf2 By implementing these interconnected recommendations, Donkey Bridge can transform its Set Wizard from a simple form into a powerful, adaptive engine for creating highly personalized, pedagogically sound, and engaging learning experiences. This involves significant changes to both backend logic (assessment, prompt engineering, data modeling) and frontend design (UI, onboarding, interaction flows). The integration of a co-creative chatbot, underpinned by robust assessment and intelligent LLM prompting, represents a key opportunity to differentiate Donkey Bridge and deliver on the promise of truly personalized and effective Thai language learning. This holistic approach, grounded in research from SLA, educational technology, and AI, will position Donkey Bridge as a cutting-edge tool for language learners.\
